132
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,200
Say something nice.

133
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,080
He would return the care.

134
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,680
The communication between people

135
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:01,400
is mutual.

136
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,400
I don't know what to say to him.

137
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,800
Say whatever you want.

138
00:11:07,800 --> 00:11:08,680
Whatever you said to me,

139
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:09,920
