146
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,280
They got no choice

147
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:31,200
but kept you at home alone.

148
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,760
Noted?

149
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,960
You know what?

150
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,480
Before I went to Shanghai,

151
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,280
Dad talked to Chief Tong

152
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,240
