169
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,400
Have a smoke.

170
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,640
I don't smoke.

171
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,960
I thought you learned to smoke

172
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,280
in Shanghai.

173
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,600
It will be all right.

174
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:32,200
After your graduation,

175
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,200
