176
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,280
We are family.

177
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:36,920
Family is complicated.

178
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,480
Well.

179
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,760
One day, I accompanied Mom to the home of

180
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:43,640
Vice President Jia of the Executive Office

181
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:44,480
