185
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,440
Do you remember her?

186
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:51,480
No.

187
00:12:51,640 --> 00:12:52,200
Really?

188
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,000
Shall I

189
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,240
