190
00:12:54,640 --> 00:12:55,680
You may want to write to her

191
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:56,880
at school.

192
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:57,680
No, thanks.

193
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,400
I don't like to write letters.

194
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,640
Don't be so absolute in what you say

195
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:03,120
before

196
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,240
