198
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:12,320
You must be thinking about

199
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,960
the policewoman in Shanghai.

200
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,000
Miss Luo told me

201
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:22,200
