202
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:24,560
You went from small talk

203
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:25,720
to ideals.

204
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,440
I was shocked.

205
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:29,960
If I'm right, except for me,

206
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:32,400
you never talk so much

207
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,200
to any other people, right?

208
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,280
And

209
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,640
Do you hit it off well?

210
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:40,760
Did she say that?

