00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,080
Our parents have arranged

220
00:14:26,080 --> 00:14:27,320
your marriage to her.

221
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,440
Brother,

222
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:32,600
