228
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:41,480
You

229
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,760
need a backer

230
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:44,160
in the Party.

231
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:45,360
So they have

232
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,000
arranged

233
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:47,920
your marriage.

