245
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,440
Brother,

246
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,440
I haven't even met

247
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,960
Vice President Jia.

248
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:18,400
How could they

249
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,920
discuss my future

250
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:21,360
and decide my life?

251
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,120
Your life

252
00:15:22,120 --> 00:15:24,200
has already been planned.

253
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,000
You are going to

254
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,200
assist the Chairman

255
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,880
in building a Revolutionary Navy.

256
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:29,760
Your romance

257
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,040
with Luo Minmin

258
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,600
