260
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:38,600
Your romance in summer

261
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,280
will disappear

262
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:39,920
before winter

263
00:15:39,920 --> 00:15:40,880
comes.

