289
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,280
His name is Peng Ganwen.

290
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,240
We just got the information

291
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,720
that he and his wife, Yao Xiulin,

292
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:35,640
have disappeared.

293
00:17:38,120 --> 00:17:40,120
It may have something to do with

294
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,880
Tan Shiyuan and the Japanese.

